title: Moving Out
itunes:title: Moving Out
description:
Hey Steve I'm a 21 year old young man that is in desperate need of advice. My father passed when I was 12 so I have very little men to choose from when it comes to advice. I am currently in a relationship that has lasted two plus years. I've even asked her to marry me and she said yes but I was thinking that I would be the one setting the pace of the relationship but she wants to move forward.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
